caption: Ordered the Nigiri Setto while having drinks at CH Distillery. Best sushi I've had in a long time! Great presentation, amazing flavors and prepared to perfection! Melted in my mouth

Wow. Where to begin! It was my first time at CH Distillery, and man did they knock it out of the park. Ambiance is inviting and cozy, with great music. Our server Cara was incredible! Very knowledgeable with all the spirits they had to offer. We decided to order off their new sushi menu offered by Jinsei Motto, and I could not be more impressed. Chef Patrick and Andrew went above and beyond in terms of quality and creativity. Every single item was absolutely sensational. I can’t imagine going anywhere else for sushi after this experience. I wish I could give more than 5 stars. Thanks again to everyone at CH and Jinsei Motto for making this an unforgettable dining experience! I cannot wait to return again and again!

Imagine a world where top flight sushi doesn’t cost more than your Xfinity bill. Imagine a Chicago where sushi is epicurean art, and not just some spicy tuna roll that looks like a tactical flashlight burglars use to crack safes. Each piece of nigiri crafted for you pays homage to timeless tradition, while flexing Chicago grit and pride at the same time. The menu is nimble and often changes based on Jinsei Motto’s ability to procure the finest ingredients for the day. This is broad-shoulder, never-miss-a-day-of-work sushi. This is sushi that belongs in the big leagues with famous names from Japan, NYC, LA....but proudly humble like the City of Chicago where Jinsei Motto was born.  Simply put, it’s amazing.
